OL,3,CWoman who killed teenagers in crash
OL,4,Cgiven more jail time
OL,6,FA woman who was speeding and sipping
OL,7,Falcohol at the wheel when she caused a
OL,8,Fcrash which killed two teenagers has
OL,9,Fhad her prison sentence increased.
OL,11,FNatasha Allarakhia was driving at
OL,12,F96mph in a 60mph zone when her Audi Q2
OL,13,Fcollided with a Ford Fiesta waiting at
OL,14,Ftemporary traffic lights on the A17
OL,15,Fnear Sleaford, Lincolnshire.
OL,17,FThe Fiesta's driver Will Ray, 17, and
OL,18,Fhis passenger and best friend, 18-year-
OL,19,Fold Eddie Shore, both died in the
OL,20,Fcrash.
