OL,3,CWoman who killed teenagers in crash
OL,4,Cgiven more jail time
OL,6,FTwo other boys were injured and taken
OL,7,Fto hospital following the incident in
OL,8,FJune last year.
OL,10,FAllarakhia, 36, admitted two counts of
OL,11,Fcausing death by dangerous driving and
OL,12,Fone of causing serious injury by
OL,13,Fdangerous driving and was jailed for
OL,14,F10 years.
OL,16,FBut the case was referred to the Court
OL,17,Fof Appeal under the Unduly Lenient
OL,18,FSentence scheme after criticism from
OL,19,Fthe victims' families.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
