OL,3,CWoman who killed teenagers in crash
OL,4,Cgiven more jail time
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, 16 December, judges at the
OL,7,Fappeal court increased the sentenced
OL,8,Fto 12 years and eight months.
OL,10,FDr Caroline Johnson, MP for Sleaford
OL,11,Fand North Hykeham, had previously said
OL,12,Fthe sentence was "woefully inadequate"
OL,13,Fand welcomed the decision to increase
OL,14,Fit.
