OL,3,CWoman who killed teenagers in crash
OL,4,Cgiven more jail time
OL,6,FShe said: "Like many people - the
OL,7,Ffamilies, friends and wider community
OL,8,Fin Sleaford - I felt the sentence
OL,9,Finitially passed was far too short for
OL,10,Fthe crime... No sentence can ever be
OL,11,Fenough, but i am pleased the sentence
OL,12,Fhas been raised today and the judge
OL,13,Frecognised the initial sentence was
OL,14,Funduly lenient."
OL,16,FLincoln Crown Court had previously
OL,17,Fheard Allarakhia had her two young
OL,18,Fdaughters in her car when the crash
OL,19,Fhappened.
