OL,3,CWoman who killed teenagers in crash
OL,4,Cgiven more jail time
OL,6,FShe lied to police at the scene for
OL,7,Fmore than an hour about who had been
OL,8,Fdriving.
OL,10,FBoth teenagers died from head
OL,11,Finjuries, shortly before they were due
OL,12,Fto receive their A-level results,
OL,13,Fwhile one of the two teenagers in the
OL,14,Fback of the car suffered severe
OL,15,Finjuries to his hip.
